## ‚òÅÔ∏è Deploy on Cloud

### üü£ Option 1: Hugging Face Spaces (Gradio UI only)

Falcon 7B is available via Inference Endpoints or Spaces:
1. Go to [https://huggingface.co/spaces](https://huggingface.co/spaces)
2. Click ‚Äú**Create new Space**‚Äù
3. Choose:
   - SDK: **Gradio**
   - Hardware: **GPU (if needed)**

4. Paste this in `app.py` (use Falcon via pipeline):
```python
import gradio as gr
from transformers import pipeline

pipe = pipeline("text-generation", model="tiiuae/falcon-7b-instruct")

def chat(input_text):
    result = pipe(input_text, max_new_tokens=150)[0]['generated_text']
    return result

gr.Interface(fn=chat, inputs="text", outputs="text", title="Falcon Chat").launch()
